            "plan": "## Prerequisite: Upgrade Commander\n\nUpgrade `commander` from `^11.0.0` (installed: 10.0.1) to `^14.0.3` in both `apps/cli` and `apps/scripts`.\n\n**Breaking changes to address:**\n- v13: excess arguments error by default вҶ’ add `.allowExcessArguments()` on the TUI default command (it uses `[prompt...]`)\n- v12: throws on duplicate option flags/command names вҶ’ shouldn't affect us since commands are distinct\n- No multi-char short flags exist in codebase вң“\n\n**New features to leverage:**\n- **Help groups** (v14): `.commandsGroup('Management Commands:')` to organize visible command output\n- **Colored help** (v13): `styleTitle()` etc. via `.configureHelp()`\n- **Dual long flags** (v13.1): `--ws, --workspace` pattern if desired\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Extract shared bootstrap into `entrypoints/bootstrap/`\n\n```\nentrypoints/bootstrap/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ index.ts              # re-exports all layers\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ core.ts              # dotenv, credentials, api/init, telemetry, sentry, tracing, shutdown coord, error handlers, i18n\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ auth.ts              # certs, auth token, orgId provider, host identity, feature flags warm\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ settings.ts          # settingsService.initialize, autonomy defaults, built-in droids\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ platform.ts          # Windows update, stale binary cleanup, console encoding\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ sandbox.ts           # sandbox service init\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ tools.ts             # task tool manager init\nв””в”Җв”Җ runtime-settings.ts  # --settings arg extraction + resolution\n```\n\nEach layer is a standalone async function. Entrypoints compose them:\n\n```ts\n// entrypoints/search/run.ts (~20 lines)\nimport { bootstrapCore } from '../bootstrap/core';\nimport { bootstrapPlatform } from '../bootstrap/platform';\nimport { bootstrapAuth } from '../bootstrap/auth';\nimport { bootstrapSettings } from '../bootstrap/settings';\n\nawait bootstrapCore();\nawait bootstrapPlatform();\nawait bootstrapAuth();\nawait bootstrapSettings();\n\nconst {